<div class ="sectionHeading" id="overview_topics"><strong>Overview of Topics</strong></div>

<p>The Topics section is where you will add links to course materials, organized into <em>topics</em>. A topic is a group of related exercises and resources. Eventually you will use your topics to create class assignments.</p>
  
<p>Before adding any content, you must ensure your course materials are hosted on <%= link_to "Connexions", "http://www.cnx.org" %> and <%= link_to "Quadbase", "http://www.quadbase.org" %>. <%= link_to_help 'plan_content' %> In addition, you should decide on the organization and sequence of the course materials you will assign. <%= link_to_help 'organize_topics' %> </p>

<div class ="sectionHeading" id="create_new_topic"><strong>Create a new topic</strong></div>
  <ol>
  <li>In the Learning Plan, under Topics, click "Add new topic...";</li>
    <center>
      <%= image_tag("newtopic1.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </center>
  <li><strong>Double click</strong> the New Topic 1 box that appears to begin adding course materials. </li>
    <center>
      <%= image_tag("newtopic5.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </center>
  </ol>
<p>
  
<div class ="sectionHeading" id="resources"><strong>Add resources to a topic</strong></div>
<p>
<ol>
  <li>Double click the topic you want to populate; </li>
  <center>
    <%= image_tag("newtopic5.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  </center>
  <li>To add resources, click "Add..." on the first line;</li>
  <center>
    <%= image_tag("add_resources.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  </center>
  <li>Copy the full URL from Connexions, paste it in the URL box, add optional resource description and notes and then click Create Resource to close;</li>
  <br/>
  <center>
    <%= image_tag("newtopic4.png", {:border => 1, :width => "40%", :height => "40%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  </center>
  <br/>
  <li>Repeat steps above as necessary.</li>  
  </ol>  
  


<div class ="sectionHeading" id="exercises"><strong>Add exercises to a topic</strong></div> 
<p>
<ol>
  <li>Double click the topic you want to populate; </li>
  <center>
    <%= image_tag("newtopic5.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  </center>
  
  <li>To add exercises, click "Add..." on the second line;</li>
  	<center>
  	  <%= image_tag("add_exercises.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  	</center>
  </li>
  <li>Copy and paste the full exercise URL from Quadbase;</li>
  <li>Mark if the exercise is reserved for a test, if applicable;</li>
  <li><%= link_to "Attach a concept tag", "#concept_tags" %>, if applicable;</li>
  <li>Save the exercise by clicking Create Topic Exercise;</li>
  <br>
  	<center>
  		<%= image_tag("newtopic6.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
  	</center>
  </li>
  <li>Repeat steps above to add as many exercises as necessary.</li>	
</ol>


<div class ="sectionHeading" id="rename_or_delete"><strong>Rename or delete a topic</strong></div>
<p>Note that you cannot delete a topic after it has been assigned.</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Hover your mouse over the name of the topic you want to edit, until the orange pencil and trash icons appear;</li>
    <center>
    <%= image_tag("newtopic5arrow.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </center>
    <li>To delete the enter topic, including associated resources/exercises, click the trash icon;</li>
    <li>To rename the topic, click the pencil icon and enter a new topic name in the text box; </li>
    <center>
    <%= image_tag("edit_topic2.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </center>
    <li>Save new topic name by hitting Enter on your keyboard.</li>
  </ol>
      <p>

<div class ="sectionHeading" id="edit_or_delete_exercise_or_resource"><strong>Edit or delete an exercise or resource from a topic </strong></div>  
<p>Note that, once a topic has been assigned to students, you cannot delete any exercises from that topic.</p>  
  <ol>
    <li>Hover your mouse over the resource or exercise you want to change, until the orange pencil and trash icons appear;</li>
    <br/>
    <center>
      <%= image_tag("edit_topic3.png", {:border => 1, :width => "60%", :height => "60%", :title=>"create new topic"})%>
    </center>
    <br/>
    <li>Click the pencil icon to open the Edit dialog box; or 
    <li>Click the trash icon to delete the item.</li>
  </ol>
<p>

